![](https://Ernket.github.io/post-images/1564568739467.png)

获取图片路径

![](https://Ernket.github.io/post-images/1564568743212.png)

然后修改php代码

```php
    public $filename_tmp="../public/upload/99afcd599914c2e4fb42620458fb70af/364be8860e8d72b4358b5e88099a935a.png";
    public $filename="/public/upload/99afcd599914c2e4fb42620458fb70af/Elapse.php";
```

执行后将生成的base64内容，通过bp发送到服务器上

![](https://Ernket.github.io/post-images/1564568749216.png)

页面报错

![](https://Ernket.github.io/post-images/1564568758857.png)

这时我们回到图片的目录下，发现名字已经更改

![](https://Ernket.github.io/post-images/1564568770184.png)
